## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification

> [!IMPORTANT]
> No automated tests exist in this project. Verification will be done via the browser.

1. Run the dev server (`npm run dev`)
2. Navigate to **Communities** → **Stays** tab
3. Click **"Arrange via SlotPilot (Paid)"** on any accommodation card
4. Verify the glassmorphic contact modal appears
5. Confirm submit button is disabled when fields are empty
6. Fill all 3 fields → button enables → submit
7. Verify success checkmark animation plays and modal auto-closes after ~2s
8. Open **Admin Dashboard** → **Stays Tasks** tab
9. Confirm the new task shows `userName`, `userEmail`, and `userPhone`
